events.name: How to Go to Market Successfully with APIs
events.description: Creating well designed APIs is only the first step to ensuring a successful API initiative. Learn how to unleash the full potential of your APIs by creating the right organization and strategies to engage with your developer community. Agenda:6:00 - 6:30 - Registration and Networking (served with drinks and canapé)6:30 - 7:15 - Introduction7:15 - 7:30 - Live Demonstration7:30 - 8:00 - Q&A  Speaker:  Tameez Sunderji is Director of Digital Strategy at TIBCO Software where he consults with customers on their digital transformation efforts. He has a background in product management, strategy, and management consulting which gives him a broad set of experiences and perspectives to bridge the business and technology worlds. Tameez holds a degree in Engineering from MIT. Please fill in the Registration form to attend.
events.location: TIBCO Software Singapore Office, 9 Raffles Place, Republic Plaza II #20-20 Singapore 48619
